Pizzelle
source|Aunt Marcella and Aunt Maureen
url|
aliases|
tags|
activeTime|
totalTime|
yield|
description|Thin cookies

# ingredients
2|sticks|butter (melted and cooled)
6||eggs
1 1/2|cup|granulated sugar
2 1/2|tbsp|anise seed
2|tsp|vailla extract
||Grated lemon peel
||Lemon juice
3|cup|sifted flour

# instructions
Beat eggs with melted butter in mixer.
Add sugar, keep beating.
Add anise seed, vanilla, and both lemon ingredients.
Slowly add sifted flour. Dont over mix.
Pour into pizzelle iron.
Optional: After beating eggs and butter, mix all ingredients by hanf, not mixer. Then pour into iron.
